# Frontend Rules

- Router and RBAC in `frontend/src/App.jsx`; API client in `frontend/src/services/api.js`.
- Pages use `fetch` or `api` with `Authorization: Bearer ${localStorage.getItem("token")}`.
- Indicator Report location order is fixed in `LOCATION_ORDER` — names must match DB `locations.name`.
- Analytics: `Overview.jsx`, `Coverage.jsx`, `Rankings.jsx`, `IndicatorReport.jsx`; Management tabs in `components/management/`.
- After upload, user must approve in Staging before reports show new committed data.
- Match year/month filters to the upload period when verifying numbers.
